WEBVTT

00:01.932 --> 00:05.688
_

00:06.069 --> 00:09.134
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

00:09.209 --> 00:12.187
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

00:12.397 --> 00:15.572
♪ Happy birthday dear, Dad ♪

00:15.637 --> 00:18.975
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

00:19.150 --> 00:20.841
That was perfect.

00:21.055 --> 00:23.282
Just perfect, thank you guys.

00:23.341 --> 00:24.777
I love you, Daddy.

00:24.789 --> 00:26.439
We miss you.

00:26.469 --> 00:29.242
- I miss you too.
- Did you get our present?

00:29.307 --> 00:30.723
Are you crazy?

00:31.069 --> 00:33.056
That's why I'm wearing it.

00:33.321 --> 00:34.581
Because I...

00:35.589 --> 00:36.969
'cause I love it.

00:37.641 --> 00:40.425
- Bye, Daddy.
- Bye-bye, I love you.

00:40.485 --> 00:42.315
Bye, guys. I love you too, and,

00:42.570 --> 00:43.889
take care!

00:46.959 --> 00:49.149
I think they forgot what you look like.

00:49.179 --> 00:51.957
I'm sorry. I know all this
travelling's been hard.

00:52.059 --> 00:53.719
Hey, how's the villa?

00:54.171 --> 00:55.575
Idyllic.

00:56.006 --> 00:58.184
At least, according to your mother.

00:58.261 --> 01:00.279
I'll say it'll be better when you get here.

01:00.669 --> 01:03.303
- You are joining us?
- Tuesday, I hope.

01:03.339 --> 01:04.985
Oh, I hope so.

01:05.703 --> 01:07.263
Maybe we can go to that

01:07.293 --> 01:08.925
seafood restaurant.

01:08.991 --> 01:10.215
Yeah.

01:10.605 --> 01:12.615
The one next to the jazz bar.

01:14.175 --> 01:15.939
With the late night cocktails.

01:16.881 --> 01:18.507
Now you're talking.

01:20.433 --> 01:22.011
Matthias, are you all right?

01:22.325 --> 01:23.667
I'm fine.

01:23.913 --> 01:25.359
You seem a little...

01:28.305 --> 01:30.599
There's someone at the
door. I'll be right back, OK?

01:30.600 --> 01:31.800
OK.

01:32.925 --> 01:34.971
Jetzt hör halt auf mal, mich zu...

01:34.989 --> 01:36.255
anzuspritzen.

01:36.273 --> 01:39.267
Kids, can you keep it down a
bit? I'm trying to talk to Papa.

01:39.268 --> 01:40.820
Jan started it.

01:40.821 --> 01:42.941
- I don't care who started it, just...
- No!

01:43.743 --> 01:44.958
No!

01:45.147 --> 01:47.139
What do you want?

01:47.145 --> 01:48.476
- No! Don't touch me!
- Matthias?

01:48.501 --> 01:49.706
Matthias?

01:49.707 --> 01:51.140
Hey, Ruhe da...

01:52.078 --> 01:53.822
- Matt?
- _

01:58.965 --> 02:00.165
Pick up.

02:01.552 --> 02:03.346
He's not picking up.

02:03.962 --> 02:07.322
Can... find the number
for the police, in Zagreb.

02:07.442 --> 02:09.289
I think... Matt's been attacked.

